data.description: ***Seller providing $10,000 seller credit!***  Qualified Buyers can receive an interest as low as 4.875% with Caliver Beach Mortgage! Contact Richard Ray  for more details.*** Discover exceptional multi-generational living in Camp Springs! This home was recently renovated (Summer 2023) and has a brand new roof, fresh paint throughout, all new appliances, hot water heater, AC Units, flooring,  and remodeled bathrooms and kitchens. Spanning three levels, and boasting a thoughtfully designed layout, the main level features a bright and open floor plan with hardwood floors, recessed lighting, and a cozy fireplace in the living and family rooms. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of cabinet space. The adjacent dining area is perfect for hosting dinner parties and family gatherings. The upper level features a spacious primary suite with a walk-in closet and a luxurious ensuite bath with dual vanities, soaking tub, and separate shower. The two additional bedrooms and den are generously sized and share a full hall bath. The lower level features a second spacious primary suite with a walk-in closet and a luxurious ensuite bath with dual vanities, soaking tub, and separate shower. The bedroom, den, and half bath create an ideal setup for guests, extended family, or a tenant with a separate living space complete with a full kitchen, living room, fireplace and laundry room. Positioned on a corner half acre lot, this property provides two distinct living areas for versatile use. Enjoy the advantage of a prime location, mere minutes from Andrews AFB, National Harbor, major highways including 495 and 295, public transit, and convenient access to Virginia. Embrace comfort, space, and convenience in this remarkable home.
